# {{brandName}}

> {{brandName}} token airdrop claim page on Solana.

## What is this

This is a {{brandName}} airdrop campaign page where eligible Solana wallet holders can claim their allocated tokens. The campaign operates on Solana {{network}} using the {{claimMode}} claim mechanism.

## How it works

1. Visit the page
2. Connect a Solana wallet (Phantom, Solflare, or any Wallet Standard compatible wallet)
3. Check eligibility — the page verifies if the connected wallet is in the recipient list
4. If eligible, view the allocated token amount and claim it
5. Sign the claim transaction to receive tokens

## Key information

- Network: Solana {{network}}
- Claim mode: {{claimMode}}
- This is a static web application — no server-side processing, no data collection
- Wallet connection is required only for claiming tokens
- All airdrop data is stored on the Solana blockchain

## Built with

This campaign page was generated by [Bonkit](https://bonkit.dev), an open-source toolkit for creating Solana airdrop campaigns.
